data.name: label11.Text
data.value: Customer appointment management(CAM) is a type of appointment scheduling software targeted towards companies with large mobile workforces that automatically routes & schedules in home services appointment arrival. The software is delivered to businesses over the internwt using the Software-as-a-service(SAAS) model. CAM software is powered by properties that learn mobile employees.

data.value: A Jewellery Shop Management, Jewellery Shop Management, or Jewellery Shop Management is a room provided for singular events such as business conferences and meetings. It is commonaly found at large Hotels and convention centers though many others establishements, including even hospitals.. Aircrafts have been fitted out with Jewellery Shop Mangement. Conference rooms can be windowless for security purposes.
